{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftdilithium\/signverify"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium"]]},"sections":[],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/KeyManagement","doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/OIDs","doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/Performance","doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/References"],"title":"Additional Information","anchor":"Additional-Information","generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"","text":"","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Messages are signed by secret keys and signatures are verified by public keys."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Signatures can be deterministic or randomized and optionally a hash of the message can be signed","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instead of the message itself."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In order to speed up signing and verifying, the secret key constructor and the public key constructor computes and caches","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a variable (called Ã‚ in FIPS 204) that is used in subsequent sign and verify operations."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"This slows down key construction but significantly improves sign and verify speed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"code":["import SwiftDilithium","","\/\/ Create keys","","let (secretKey, publicKey) = Dilithium.GenerateKeyPair(kind: .ML_DSA_44)","","\/\/ Deterministic signature","let deterministicSig = secretKey.Sign(message: [1, 2, 3], randomize: false)","print(\"Deterministic:\", publicKey.Verify(message: [1, 2, 3], signature: deterministicSig))","","\/\/ Randomized signature","let randomizedSig = secretKey.Sign(message: [1, 2, 3], randomize: true)","print(\"Randomized:\", publicKey.Verify(message: [1, 2, 3], signature: randomizedSig))","","\/\/ Prehashed signature","let prehashedSig = secretKey.Sign(message: [1, 2, 3], ph: .SHAKE128)","print(\"Prehashed:\", publicKey.Verify(message: [1, 2, 3], signature: prehashedSig, ph: .SHAKE128))"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"giving:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["Deterministic: true","Randomized: true","Prehashed: true"]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/SignVerify"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"SwiftDilithium"}],"role":"article","title":"Sign and Verify"},"references":{"doc://SwiftDilithium/documentation/SwiftDilithium":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftdilithium","abstract":[{"text":"Module-Lattice-Based Digital Signature Standard","type":"text"}],"title":"SwiftDilithium","type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium"},"doc://SwiftDilithium/documentation/SwiftDilithium/References":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/References","title":"References","role":"article","url":"\/documentation\/swiftdilithium\/references","kind":"article"},"doc://SwiftDilithium/documentation/SwiftDilithium/Performance":{"abstract":[],"kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/swiftdilithium\/performance","title":"Performance","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/Performance"},"doc://SwiftDilithium/documentation/SwiftDilithium/KeyManagement":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftDilithium\/documentation\/SwiftDilithium\/KeyManagement","title":"Key Management","role":"article","kin